post_cb({"23907478": {"CommentCount": "3", "ViewCount": "51", "LastActivityDate": "2014-05-29T08:58:00.173", "Body": "<pre><code>int a;//1\n\nint main()\n{\n    int a;//2\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>As said in 3.4/1:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p id=\"so_23907478_23907478_0\">The name lookup rules apply uniformly to all names (including\n  typedef-names (7.1.3), namespace-names (7.3), and class-names (9.1))</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Thus, for <code>//2</code> declaration name lookup will be applied. What name will be found?</p>\n", "PostTypeId": "1", "AcceptedAnswerId": "23908369", "FavoriteCount": "1", "Title": "Application of name lookup to just declared name", "Id": "23907478", "Score": "-1", "CreationDate": "2014-05-28T09:16:42.127", "Tags": "<c++><declaration>", "OwnerUserId": "2786156", "AnswerCount": "1"}, "23908369": {"ParentId": "23907478", "LastEditDate": "2014-05-29T08:58:00.173", "CommentCount": "4", "CreationDate": "2014-05-28T09:55:00.713", "OwnerUserId": "3647361", "LastEditorUserId": "3647361", "PostTypeId": "2", "Id": "23908369", "Score": "1", "Body": "<blockquote>\n<p id=\"so_23907478_23908369_0\">What name will be found?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>The only thing possibly looked at will be the <em>declarative region</em>, to check whether <code>a</code> is not redeclared invalidly. Obviously nothing will be found.</p>\n<p>Moreover, there is no such thing as (unqualified) name lookup done while declaring names, rather when using them. The standard says nothing about unqualified name lookup for names being declared, rather for names used in specific contexts, such as a name as a postfix-expression for a function call. In particular, names being declared have to satisfy certain conditions, whether they are local, in class or in namespace scope; it is beyound this post to list them all up.</p>\n", "LastActivityDate": "2014-05-29T08:58:00.173"}, "bq_ids": {"n4140": {"so_23907478_23907478_0": {"section_id": 7083, "quality": 0.8461538461538461, "length": 11}}, "n3337": {"so_23907478_23907478_0": {"section_id": 6827, "quality": 0.8461538461538461, "length": 11}}, "n4659": {"so_23907478_23907478_0": {"section_id": 8584, "quality": 0.8461538461538461, "length": 11}}}});